name: Spider-Man
plot: When a new villain threatens New York City, Peter Parker and Spider-Man's worlds collide. To save the city and those he loves, he must rise up and be greater.

name: Red Dead Redemption II
plot: Amidst the decline of the Wild West at the turn of the 20th century, outlaw Arthur Morgan and his gang struggle to cope with the loss of their way of life.

name: Grand Theft Auto V
plot: Three very different criminals team up for a series of heists and walk into some of the most thrilling experiences in the corrupt city of Los Santos.

name: God of War
plot: After wiping out the gods of Mount Olympus, Kratos moves on to the frigid lands of Scandinavia, where he and his son must embark on an odyssey across a dangerous world of gods and monsters.

name: Uncharted 4: A Thief's End
plot: Thrown back into the dangerous underworld he'd tried to leave behind, Nathan Drake must decide what he's willing to sacrifice to save the ones he loves.

name: The Last of Us: Part II
plot: Five years after the events of The Last of Us, Ellie embarks on another journey through a post-apocalyptic America on a mission of vengeance against a mysterious militia.

name: Horizon Forbidden West
plot: Aloy treks into an arcane region and faces new hostile enemies and threats in search of a way to heal the world from a deadly blight and catastrophic storms.

name: The Last of Us
plot: In a hostile, post-pandemic world, Joel and Ellie, brought together by desperate circumstances, must rely on each other to survive a brutal journey across what remains of the United States.

name: Detroit: Become Human
plot: Take control of three androids in their quest to discover who they really are.

name: Death Stranding

name: Ghost of Tsushima

name: Spider-Man: Miles Morales
plot: In this sequel of Marvel's Spider-Man (2018), you can play as Miles Morales as a new and different Spider-Man while he learns some stories about his will of fighting crime and serving justice by his mentor and former hero, Peter Parker.

name: Cyberpunk 2077
plot: In Night City, a mercenary known as V navigates a dystopian society in which the line between humanity and technology becomes blurred.

name: Uncharted: Drake's Fortune
plot: Treasure hunter Nathan Drake, embarks in the adventure of his life searching for the legendary treasure, El Dorado while fighting a group of mercenaries.

name: Batman: Arkham Knight
plot: With his back against the wall, Batman turns to his closest allies to help him save Gotham City from the clutches of Scarecrow and the Arkham Knight's army. A familiar face also returns to give The Dark Knight a message he cannot ignore.

name: Far Cry 6
plot: As dictator of Yara, Anton Castillo is intent on restoring his nation back to its former glory by any means, with his son, Diego, following in his bloody footsteps.

name: Grand Theft Auto: San Andreas
plot: A family tragedy prompts gangster Carl "CJ" Johnson to return home, only to find it overrun by crime and corruption, which he must regain control of the streets before it gets even worse.

name: MultiVersus
plot: A crossover fighting game featuring many different Warner Bros properties.

name: Far Cry 3
plot: While skydiving, Jason Brody and his friends land on an island overrun by pirates, where Jason is torn between fighting for the Rakyat resistance and rescuing his friends.

name: Star Wars Jedi: Fallen Order
plot: Set shortly after Revenge of the Sith, the player takes on the role of a Jedi padawan being hunted by the Empire after Order 66.

name: Elden Ring
plot: In a dark fantasy world created by Hidetaka Miyazaki (Dark Souls) and George R. R. Martin (A Song of Ice and Fire), the player is a Tarnished who is called back to the Lands Between to restore the Elden Ring and become the Elden Lord.

name: Xenoblade Chronicles 3
plot: In the world of Aionios, two nations are locked in conflict: Keves, a technological powerhouse and Agnus, a magic-based society. Six soldiers hailing from these nations, will take part in a grand tale with life as its central theme.

name: Uncharted: The Nathan Drake Collection
plot: A remastered collection of Uncharted: Drake's Fortune (2007), Uncharted 2: Among Thieves (2009), and Uncharted 3: Drake's Deception (2011) for PlayStation 4.

name: Assassin's Creed Valhalla
plot: England in the age of the Vikings is a fractured nation of petty lords and warring kingdoms. Beneath the chaos lies a rich and untamed land waiting for a new conqueror. Will it be you?

name: Marvel's Guardians of the Galaxy
plot: After an epic conflict known as the Galactic War swept through the cosmos. Star-Lord recently formed the Guardians of the Galaxy, they've been together for less than a year.

name: Grand Theft Auto: Vice City
plot: After being released from jail, Tommy Vercetti left Liberty City for Vice City, a city overrun by the mob. Now, Tommy is out to make Vice City his home.

name: Uncharted 2: Among Thieves
plot: After being tracked down by Harry Flynn, Nathan Drake goes on a quest for Marco Polo's lost fleet. However when things take an unexpected turn for the worst, Drake must rely on those closest to him in order to find the Cintomani Stone.

name: The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt
plot: A monster hunter for hire embarks on an epic journey to find his former apprentice before The Wild Hunt can capture her and bring about the destruction of the world.

name: Fallout: New Vegas
plot: After surviving a bullet to the head, Courier Six traverses the post-apocalyptic Mojave desert in search of the men who wronged him, while making an impact on thousands in the process.

name: Command & Conquer: Red Alert 3

name: Horizon Zero Dawn

name: Red Dead Redemption
plot: A former outlaw is forced by the federal government to hunt down the members of his old gang.

name: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare

name: Final Fantasy VII Remake

name: Genshin Impact

name: The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim
plot: After escaping execution, the last living Dragonborn must grow in strength and power to defeat the dragons that have once again begun to plague the land of Skyrim.

name: Fallout 4

name: Yakuza: Like a Dragon

name: Days Gone
plot: Two years after a devastating global pandemic, bounty hunter Deacon St. John faces a brutal struggle for survival, and a reason to live.

name: Grand Theft Auto IV
plot: Niko Bellic comes to Liberty City, America to live the good life, but ends up having to assist his dangerously indebted cousin Roman with his financial troubles, by any (mostly illegal) means necessary.

name: Batman: Arkham City
plot: When part of Gotham is turned into a private reserve for criminals known as Arkham City, all hell is sure to break loose, and the Dark Knight is the only one who can stop it.

name: Tiny Tina's Wonderlands
plot: Embark on an epic adventure full of whimsy, wonder, and high-powered weaponry. Bullets, magic, and broadswords collide across this chaotic fantasy world brought to life by the unpredictable Tiny Tina.

name: Saints Row
plot: An international private military corporation based in Santo Ileso that provides security for the city.

name: Marvel's Avengers

name: Assassin's Creed: Odyssey

name: Far Cry 5

name: Resident Evil Village
plot: Ethan Winters' world suddenly comes crashing down when Chris Redfield's appearance sets off a chain of events that ultimately leads him to a mysterious village.

name: L.A. Noire
plot: Cole Phelps, a war hero and rookie cop, moves up the ranks and solves dark cases in 1940s Los Angeles.

name: Fortnite
plot: A cooperative shooter-survival game for up to four players to fight off zombie-like husks, defend objects with fortifications you can build, and a battle royale mode where up to 100 players fight to be the last person standing.

name: The Dark Pictures: House of Ashes
plot: A group of American marines comes across an underground nest of pure, ancient evil while trekking through the Arabian desert.

name: Mortal Kombat 11
plot: When a time lord starts merging past with the present, versions of heroes from both Mortal Kombat timelines must unite to right past wrongs and save the world.

name: Batman: Arkham Asylum
plot: You control Batman as he fights to subdue The Joker and his fellow inmates when they seize control of the Asylum on Arkham Island.

name: Lego Star Wars: The Skywalker Saga
plot: Play through all nine Star Wars films in a LEGO Game of epic proportions.

name: Assassin's Creed IV: Black Flag
plot: A video game where you play as sailor, privateer and assassin Edward Kenway exploring on and around the islands in the Caribbean Sea during the early 17th century.

name: Injustice 2

name: Predator: Hunting Grounds
plot: Survive the Predator's hunt or hunt down a fire-team.

name: Uncharted 3: Drake's Deception
plot: Treasure hunter Nathan Drake embarks on a quest in search of the Atlantis of the Sands while battling an ancient, sinister organization.

name: Mass Effect
plot: In a technologically advanced future, an elite human soldier takes command of a prototype star ship and works to defend the galaxy from danger.

name: Assassin's Creed II
plot: Desmond Miles is trained to become a modern-day Assassin through the resurrected memories of ancestor Ezio Auditore da Firenze, who uncovers a massive Templar conspiracy in Renaissance Italy leading to the new Pope.

name: Mass Effect 2
plot: After being revived from death and having to join a pro-human organization without a choice, Commander Shepard must assemble a team, battle a new threat, and make tough choices in order to save the galaxy from total annihilation once more.

name: Metal Gear Solid V: The Phantom Pain

name: Apex Legends
plot: Master an ever-growing roster of legendary characters with powerful abilities and experience strategic squad play and innovative gameplay in the next evolution of Hero Shooter and Battle Royale.

name: Tomb Raider
plot: Armed with only the raw instincts and physical ability, experience Lara Croft's intense origin story from a young woman to a hardened survivor.

name: Ghost Recon: Wildlands

name: Saints Row: The Third
plot: After the Saints have transformed from a small town street gang to pop culture giants, they decide to take over another city called Steelport.

name: Cuphead

name: Poppy Playtime
plot: In this horror/puzzle adventure, You must survive the vengeful toys waiting for you in the abandoned toy factory, Use your GrabPack and Explore the mysterious facility.. and don't get caught.

name: Control

name: Assassin's Creed: Origins

name: God of War III
plot: Armed with his deadly double-chained blades, Kratos must take on Greek mythology's darkest creatures to destroy Olympus and the mighty Zeus himself.

name: Mass Effect: Legendary Edition
plot: A compilation of the first three Mass Effect games.

name: Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2

name: Call of Duty: Vanguard

name: Minecraft

name: Resident Evil VII: Biohazard
plot: An ordinary man must embark on a search to find his missing wife that leads him to an abandoned house where a mysterious family lives who harbor an evil secret within the house and themselves.

name: Metal Gear Rising: Revengeance

name: Call of Duty: WWII

name: God of War
plot: After 10 years of endless nightmares and servitude to the gods of Olympus, Kratos is assigned with a final task, to kill Ares, the God of War.

name: Saints Row IV
plot: Play as your own customized President of United States of America and fight for an Alien invasion that nobody saw coming.

name: Resident Evil 2
plot: Re-imagining of Resident Evil 2 (1998), with a third-person over-the-shoulder view, new details, rearranged and new areas, no more loading screen doors, new puzzle solving opportunities, a gunpowder crafting mechanic and more.

name: Grand Theft Auto III
plot: A young bank robber escapes from police custody and works his way up through the mafia ladder of crime-ridden Liberty City, USA.

name: BioShock Infinite
plot: A man is sent to the flying city of Columbia to find a missing girl. However, upon arrival he discovers that the city, its people, and his objective are all not what they seem.

name: Mass Effect: Andromeda
plot: The Andromeda Initiative sets a course for a new galaxy, hoping to find a new home for the species of the Milky Way.

name: Fortnite: Chapter 3
plot: The Island has flipped. The Foundation is seeking help from the Loopers and Agent Jones helps him and The Seven reunite and find Geno.

name: The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild
plot: After a century of hibernation, Link reawakens to once again save a ruined Hyrule from a great evil.

name: Watch Dogs 2
plot: In San Francisco, hacker Marcus Holloway joins DedSec, to take down a corrupt system by fighting and hacking his way through the entire San Francisco Bay.

name: Saints Row 2
plot: Several new upstart gangs have been able to sweep in and make their mark on Stilwater. As leader of the Saints, you'll have to do whatever it takes to protect the members of your gang.

plot: Set during the early 80s of the Cold War, the campaign follows CIA operative Russel Adler as he pursues an alleged Soviet spy, whose goal is to subvert the United States and tilt the balance of power towards the Soviet Union.

plot: When all hope is lost and humanity's fate hangs in the balance, Master Chief is ready to confront the most ruthless foe he's ever faced.

name: Fallout 3
plot: Centuries following nuclear war, a teen leaves the safety of an underground vault in order to find their father, who left in hopes of creating a water purifier.

name: Mafia III

name: Beyond: Two Souls
plot: Live the life of Jodie Holmes, a young woman who possesses supernatural powers through her psychic link to a mysterious invisible entity.

name: Mafia II

plot: First-person action survival game set in a post-apocalyptic open world overrun by flesh-hungry zombies. Roam a city devastated by a mysterious virus epidemic. Scavenge for supplies, craft weapons, and face hordes of the infected.

plot: When a mysterious and powerful vortex appears in various lego worlds, Batman, Gandalf and Wyldstyle bravely jump into the vortex and travel through space and time to rescue their friends.

plot: Kiryu and Majima, both Yakuza's who are in different cities in Japan in 1988, as the fate of the two characters become intertwined in a gritty, violent, and often touching narrative.

name: Bully
plot: A troubled teen is dropped off at the worst school in the country and must survive by rising through the rankings of the school system.

name: Quantum of Solace
plot: James Bond battles the evil Quantum organization as well as a new enemy.

plot: 007 and Serena St. Germaine discover that Katya Nadonova's project, nanobots designed to repair nuclear reactors; have been stolen by Nikolai Diavolo. Together the two set off to new Orleans and beyond to confront Diavolo.

name: Devil May Cry 5
plot: Years have passed since the legions of hell have set foot in this world, but now a new demonic invasion has begun, and humanity's last hope will rest in the hands of three lone demon hunters, each offering a radically different play style.

name: Bloodborne
plot: A hunter awakens in the plagued lands of Yharnam, where the denizens have succumb to beast hood, in an attempt to learn the truth and how to end the plague, unbeknownst of the true horror lurking within the city.

name: God of War II
plot: After being betrayed by the gods of Olympus and annulled of his divine powers, Kratos must embark on a journey to meet the Sisters of Fate and take his revenge on Olympus.

name: Call of Duty: Black Ops II
plot: Set in 2025, new unmanned machines have been taken over by Nicaraguan terrorist, Raul Menendez, forcing the U.S.A. to take action.

name: Sleeping Dogs

plot: Spider-Man/Peter Parker struggles between his personal life which involves Mary Jane Watson and his superhero life where he joins up with a vigilante known as Black Cat battling a series of foes including the mad Doc Ock.

name: Sekiro: Shadows Die Twice

name: Middle-Earth: Shadow of War

name: Overwatch
plot: After a devastating war against a combat-ready team of intelligent machines known as Omnics, the former agents of the heroic team known as Overwatch must join forces once more to fight a new threat.

name: James Bond: World of Espionage
plot: No Plot

name: Hitman 3
plot: Together with Diana Burnwood and Lucas Grey, Agent 47 must face off against The Constant and his mysterious colleagues to take down Providence once and for all.

name: Resident Evil
plot: The RPD are investigating strange cannibalized corpses on the outskirts of the city. The Alpha squad, Jill and Chris, are sent to locate missing team members. While there, mutated dogs cause them to flee into a supposedly abandoned mansion.

name: Doom

name: Watch Dogs
plot: After losing his niece in an assassination attempt, Aiden Pierce, a street-smart vigilante, uses hacking apps on his phone to take over a new operating system in Chicago to hunt the criminals that killed his niece.

name: Halo 2
plot: As the alien Covenant invade Earth, the Master Chief must defend humanity's homeworld whilst discovering more about the rings called "Halo."

name: Prey

name: GTAV
plot: Four very different criminals team up for a series of heists and walk into some of the most thrilling experiences in the corrupt city of Los Santos.

name: Star Wars: Battlefront II
plot: A game based on the Star Wars Universe, taking place across multiple eras of the franchise.

name: Scarface: The World Is Yours
plot: Scarface the game begins during the final scene of the film, with the mansion of Tony Montana under attack from assassins sent by Alejandro Sosa. When Tony survives, his quest to kill Sosa begins.

name: Saints Row
plot: In Saints Row you start as a member of the 3rd Street Saints, a gang that is under attack from three other gangs that dominate the city of Stilwater. In order to survive, you have to take over their strongholds, and kill the gang kingpins.

name: Destiny 2: The Witch Queen
plot: Take back the light from Savath√ªn in an all-new story.

name: Metal Gear Solid
plot: A crack government anti-terrorist squad takes over an obscure Alaskan nuclear disposal facility. Solid Snake is up for the task to infiltrate the facility, rescue the two hostages and thwart the terrorists' plans.

name: DC League of Super-Pets: The Adventures of Krypto and Ace
plot: Puts players in the paws of Super-Pets Krypto the Super-Dog and Ace as they take to the skies to protect the animal population of Metropolis from a new and looming threat.

name: The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion
plot: After being freed by the Emperor of Tamriel, the hero must prevent the gates of Oblivion from spreading throughout the Empire.

name: Ghost Recon: Breakpoint
plot: You are sent to Auroa for what seems to a be a typical recon mission, but your helicopter is shot down. The island has fallen into the wrong hands.

name: Resident Evil 3
plot: Re-imagining of Resident Evil 3: Nemesis (1999). Jill Valentine escapes the crumbling Raccoon City amidst the nightmarish outbreak of the T-virus, a biological weapon developed by Umbrella, while being pursued by the unrelenting bioweapon Nemesis.

name: Shadow of the Tomb Raider
plot: As Lara Croft races to save the world from a Mayan apocalypse, she must become the Tomb Raider she is destined to be.

name: Dishonored
plot: After being framed for the murder of the Empress he swore to protect, a once trusted bodyguard with supernatural abilities is forced to become a masked assassin in order to seek revenge on those who conspired against him.

name: Assassin's Creed
plot: A man enters a machine called the Animus that lets him relive the memories of his ancestor, a 12th century assassin named Altair.

name: Star Wars: The Old Republic

name: Spider-Man 3
plot: Spider-Man is back to save the city with his usual hero work, only this time he bonds with an alien substance known as symbiote which turns his hero days and personal life into something ugly.

name: Ratchet & Clank: Rift Apart

name: Assassin's Creed: Brotherhood

name: Half-Life 2
plot: Dr. Freeman is taken out of stasis by his "employer" to help rid the planet of invading aliens forces known as the Combine that entered through the portals he helped create.

name: Dota 2
